**1. Definitions.**

    "Individual Use" shall mean use of the Project by a natural person for their personal, 

non-commercial streaming activities, including those where viewers may contribute financially

(e.g., via Twitch bits, YouTube Super Chats). This explicitly excludes use by or on behalf 

of any commercial entity.


    "Commercial Use" shall mean any use of the Project by or on behalf of a business, company, 

organization, or any other legal entity, for any purpose, whether direct or indirect,

that generates revenue, profit, or other commercial gain.



**2. Permitted Use (Individual Use Only)**:

The author explicitly allows this Project to be used for Individual Use on live streaming

platforms that are specifically accessible to the public as platforms with 

primary or major sub-functionality featuring the live streaming/sharing of productions and 

works created by members of the public (such as Twitch, YouTube, Kick, etc.).


For Individual Use, you may use, duplicate, store, modify the Project or

parts thereof, and create and distribute derivative works based on the Project,

provided the modified/derivative versions also adhere to the terms of this

license and provide attribution.



