Any **Commercial Use** of the Project is strictly **prohibited** without the express written permission and a separate commercial license from the author. Contact the author at aerohyena@proton.me for commercial license requests.

Additionally, regardless of user type, you may not:
* Sell, license, or integrate the Project itself into a paid service (other than permitted Individual Use monetization on live streaming platforms).
* Sublicense this Project to third parties.
* Use the trade names, trademarks, service marks, or product names of the Author, except as required for reasonable and customary use in describing the origin of the Project and reproducing the content of the NOTICE/README files.

Contact the author at aerohyena@proton.me for permissions and licensing requests.



